description:
GNOME 46.1 is now available as the first point release to the latest GNOME 46 desktop environment series introducing explicit sync support, as well as various other improvements.

The post GNOME 46.1 Desktop Environment Released with Explicit Sync Support appeared first on 9to5Linux - do not reproduce this article without permission. This RSS feed is intended for readers, not scrapers.
title: GNOME 46.1 Desktop Environment Released with Explicit Sync Support
